{{ 'product-litter.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<div class="product-litter page-width">
  <div class="litter-img">
    <picture>
      <source media="(min-width: 901px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.image_1 }}">
      <source media="(max-width: 900px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.m_image_1 }}">
      <img src="{{ section.settings.image_1 }}" alt="petsnowy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
    </picture>
  </div>

  <div class="litter-2">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="litter-content">
        <p class="litter-title">
          A Fresh Start to<br>
          Your Morning Routine
        </p>
        <P class="litter-desc">
          Everyday, PetSnowy filters out unwanted litters and maintains a clean, hygienic place for your cats.Want to
          change the whole litter bed?With just one click or a tap on your phone,PetSnowy will dump and pack it up for
          you.
        </P>
      </div>
      <picture>
        <source media="(min-width: 901px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.image_2 }}">
        <source media="(max-width: 900px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.m_image_2 }}">
        <img src="{{ section.settings.image_2 }}" alt="petsnowy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
      </picture>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="litter-3">
    <div class="container">
      <picture>
        <source media="(min-width: 901px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.image_3 }}">
        <source media="(max-width: 900px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.m_image_3 }}">
        <img src="{{ section.settings.image_3 }}" alt="petsnowy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
      </picture>
      <div class="litter-content">
        <p class="litter-title">You have cats AND your house smells good!</p>
        <P class="litter-desc">
          <span class="special">3-Stage Deodorization</span> TiO2 System <span class="thick">decomposes</span> bacteria
          and fungi Robertet Fragrance <span class="thick">neutralizes</span> smelly factorsEnclosed structure
          <span class="thick">contains</span> the odor
        </P>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="litter-4">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="litter-content">
        <p class="litter-title">
          Pull to pack<br>
          trap in odors and dust
        </p>
        <P class="litter-desc">
          Patented self-packing design automatically pack the waste for you so you can keep your hands and your nose
          clean.Avoid direct exposure to the harm and the foul!lt's self-pack yet not sealed so you can still check on
          your catsâ€™ health if you want.
        </P>
      </div>
      <picture>
        <source media="(min-width: 901px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.image_4 }}">
        <source media="(max-width: 900px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.m_image_4 }}">
        <img src="{{ section.settings.image_4 }}" alt="petsnowy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
      </picture>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="litter-5">
    <div class="container">
      <picture>
        <source media="(min-width: 901px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.image_5 }}">
        <source media="(max-width: 900px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.m_image_5 }}">
        <img src="{{ section.settings.image_5 }}" alt="petsnowy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
      </picture>
      <div class="litter-content">
        <p class="litter-title">
          Max the good,<br>
          nix the bad.<br>
          More details <br>
          Less work
        </p>
        <P class="litter-desc">
          *Anti-tracking curved walkway design,keeps the litter in and your floor clean.Trap litter at its source with
          the included walkway mat that's gentle on your cats feet.
        </P>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="litter-6">
    <div class="container">
      <picture>
        <source media="(min-width: 901px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.image_6 }}">
        <source media="(max-width: 900px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.m_image_6 }}">
        <img src="{{ section.settings.image_6 }}" alt="petsnowy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
      </picture>
      <div class="litter-content">
        <P class="litter-desc">
          * PetSnowy's magnetic assembly design maxed the good and nixed the bad.Assembling and disassembling could be a
          breeze.The machine is super low-maintenance,with no need to worry about any components falling off,minimizing
          wear and tear.
        </P>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

